{"tid":1509580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【前線手足】下次反黑果陣可唔可以大叫triad","createTime":"2019-08-27T01:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T01:49:00.000Z","uid":221192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc64b03822ca6f6b77f693e838732a841516b294","tid":1509580,"uid":221192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:42:28.000Z","msg":"琴日睇到呢段片 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/videos/422329445048555/?v=422329445048555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcityusu.cbc%2Fvideos%2F422329445048555%2F%3Fv%3D422329445048555&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=ead4a2ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/videos/422329445048555/?v=422329445048555</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然facebook呢個post係有文字解說（以噴漆於店門寫上「黑社會」、期間有附近商店落閘，示威者向他們解釋不會攻擊平民開的舖頭，該商店店員向示威者豎起拇指並繼續營業），但淨係睇片其實唔明顯，外國記者要報道係有難度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我發夢下次可唔可以係更加當眼既位置噴返英文 TRIAD ？例如拆完招牌之後，噴返落佢個招牌位度，咁樣第二日行過路過d街坊一眼就知道咩事啦。同埋一路拆一路用英文大叫 TRIAD，咁條片拍出黎都會更有效果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a0aa3784d677fe548e482d81008d8544e1372e","tid":1509580,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:42:52.000Z","msg":"小知識 - 原來機場控制唔只控制香港D機上落，<br />\n廣洲，深圳，澳門既飛機升降都會受香港指揮影響，搞到D飛升降唔到。。。。<br />\n大家千祈唔好搞到機場控制個班番唔到工啊 會好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3F